  "notes": "Repress from the 2015 release. Artwork and 7 inserts, all the same. Only difference on both labels. No old MPO \"rings\" present. \n\nIncludes download code for entire album plus the tracks \"Realiti\" and \"REALiTi (Demo)\", minus the track \"Butterfly\".  Release includes 14 art prints designed by Grimes. Gatefold sleeve.\n\n\"Butterfly\" contains a sample from \"Penguin Dancer\" co-written by Masayoshi Takanaka and Shu Suzuki.\n\nJanelle Monáe appears courtesy of Wondaland/Atlantic Recording Corporation.",
